               <p>The Prosecutor depos'd. That the Prisoner took a Room Furnished of her Weekly, and that on the 16th of March last she took her Opportunity to carry of the Goods aforesaid; and being afterwards taken she confes'd the Fact, and gave the Prosecutor a Note where she might find them. The Jury brought her in <rs id="t17270412-22-verdict110" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17270412-22-verdict110" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
